Mariem Alaoui Selsouli (Arabic, amụrụ na Julaị 8, na afọ 1984) bụ onye Morocco na-agba ọsọ n'etiti na ogologo oge
Na afo 2009 World Athletics Final na Berlin, Selsouli si na 1500m ikpeazụ pụọ mgbe ọ dara ule ọgwụ maka EPO. IAAF kwụsịtụrụ ya afọ abụọ, site na Ougost 22, na afọ 2009 ruo ougustu 21, na afọ 2011

Na Julaị 23, na afọ 2012 a machibidoro ya iwu na Summer Olympics na London mgbe ọ nwalere na ọ bụ furosemide diuretic, na-eso asọmpi ya na Diamond league na Julaị 6, na afọ 2012 na Paris-Saint-Denis. A machibidoro ya iwu ọgwụ ọjọọ afọ asatọ site na 6 Julaị , na afọ 2012 ruo 24 Julaị, na afọ 2020.
